\end_inset

 and sweep to the right, resulting in the following sequence
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{H}=\boldsymbol{ð}\hat{W}^{1}\hat{W}^{2}\hat{W}^{3}\cdots\hat{W}^{N-1}\hat{W}^{N}\boldsymbol{ð}
\]

